	<p>
    <div style="clear:both;"></div><p>What <em>is</em> Arnold up to?&nbsp; Made me look too.</p><p>It was the local weekly and I was crossing California Avenue when I noticed the headline in the newspaper box (what <em>do</em> they call those things with the coin-operated doors?).&nbsp; Had me for a moment.&nbsp; How about you?</p><p align="center">{tag: <a href="http://technorati.com/tag/orcmid" rel="tag">orcmid</a> <a href="http://technorati.com/tag/California" rel="tag">California</a> <a href="http://technorati.com/tag/West+Seattle" rel="tag">West Seattle</a>}</p><div style="clear:both; padding-bottom: 0.25em;"></div>
